para_trans: Regarding the release of final seniority of Construction Engineering Assistant cadre employees of the field office under the Water Resources Department for the period 2019 to 2023 AT.
Government Certificate No. - Seniority - 1424 / Q. 25 / Aastha (Technical)

Read: - 1) Department of Water Resources, Government Circular No. Seniority-1424 / Q. 25 / Aastha (Technical), D. 06.02.2025 2) Department of Water Resources, Government Circular No. Seniority-1424 / P.No.25 / Aastha (Technical), Govt. 28.03.2025

Government Certificate: - Government Reference No. 1 of Interim Seniority of Construction Engineers Assistant Cadre employees of the Field Office under the Department of Water Resources from 1st January, 2019 to 31st December, 2019, from 1st January, 2020 to 31st December, 2020, from 1st January, 2021 to 31st December, 2021, from 1st January, 2022 to 31st December, 2022 and from 9th January, 2023 to 31st December, 2023. The date 1 is published here by the circular 06.02.2025. Also, the last seniority reference No. 2 is published by the circular dated 28.03.2025.

Proposals / requests for revision in the final seniority list of Architectural Engineers Assistant have been received from the Board of Applications Office. Accordingly, the service details of the concerned Architectural Engineers Assistant are being revised as per Annexure-A after scrutinizing / scrutinizing the application after receipt of proposal and service seniority of the concerned Architectural Engineers Assistant as per Annexure-B.
The government certificate is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra, www.maharashtra.gov.in.
